Package: copulaNetworks
Title: Stratified Nonparanormal Copula Networks
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("GW", "McElfresh", email = "mcelfreshgw@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fit and visualize stratified nonparanormal Gaussian copula
    graphical models using graphical lasso (glasso) with StARS model
    selection. Supports declarative stratification, single-stratum
    diagnostics, and cross-stratum structure comparison. v0.4.0 adds
    Bayesian meta-analysis of multiple historical cohorts via multivariate
    power priors (powerprior package) with small-sample graphical update.
    v0.3.0 adds a two-phase factor-vine workflow (large-sample factor copula
    prior plus small-sample graphical or vine update) with simulation and
    optional Bayesian consistency testing.
